title: Grateful Dead Live at Nassau Coliseum on 1990-03-28
lineage: Dat > Sony PCM r500 > Tascam DA-3000 > Flac 16/48
description:
Set 1

Cold Rain & Snow, Minglewood Blues, Easy To Love You, High Time, Queen Jane Approximately, Loose Lucy, Cassidy, Deal

Set 2

Foolish Heart, Looks Like Rain, Cumberland Blues, The Weight, Hey Pocky Way, Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Good Lovin', E: Revolution

FM Broadcast on WPYX
